Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:28.88,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fnFOT-Greco Std B\fad(300,300)}閉ざされてきた　ゲート「規制」は終わった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:30.06,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fnFOT-Greco Std B\fad(300,300)}Open The Eyes――
