Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:41.56,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fnFOT-Greco Std B\fad(300,300)}Open The Eyes――
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:47.15,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fnFOT-Greco Std B\fad(300,300)}宇宙がまだ隠し持った　秩序のない理論
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:55.90,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fnFOT-Greco Std B\fad(300,300)}無限と呼ばれた点と点が　不正な力を借りて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:58.90,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fnFOT-Greco Std B\fad(300,300)}「再生」をする
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:12.30,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fnFOT-Greco Std B\fad(300,300)}「0」が過去で　「1」が未来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:23.45,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fnFOT-Greco Std B\fad(300,300)}並行する無数の線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:35.98,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fnFOT-Greco Std B\fad(300,300)}「0」が過去で　「1」が未来　「今」は何処にもない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:40.96,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fnFOT-Greco Std B\fad(300,300)}背く事の出来ぬ　ロジック
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:41.96,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fnFOT-Greco Std B\fad(300,300)}Open The Eyes――
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:47.44,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fnFOT-Greco Std B\fad(300,300)}並行する無数の線　選択は冒涜へ
