Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:11.60,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur3\fnFOT-MatisseV Pro B\fad(300,300)}ただ刷り込まれたビジョン
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:22.94,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur3\fnFOT-MatisseV Pro B\fad(300,300)}無限遠点　価値観を今　上書きする　変哲の無い宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:33.12,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur3\fnFOT-MatisseV Pro B\fad(300,300)}傲慢な神は　目に映らない　光速度で　支配続けるならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:41.50,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur3\fnFOT-MatisseV Pro B\fad(300,300)}僕は　僕だけは　奇跡的で　致命的な
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:45.05,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur3\fnFOT-MatisseV Pro B\fad(300,300)}マイノリティでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:46.55,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur3\fnFOT-MatisseV Pro B\fad(300,300)}I can fly───
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:52.06,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur3\fnFOT-MatisseV Pro B\fad(300,300)}あの瞬間、あの場面が　キミにとって特別なら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:57.23,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur3\fnFOT-MatisseV Pro B\fad(300,300)}過去は離れて　行くものなんかじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:23:02.65,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur3\fnFOT-MatisseV Pro B\fad(300,300)}傷つく事の痛みより　大事なシーン　その全ての
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:07.82,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur3\fnFOT-MatisseV Pro B\fad(300,300)}ヒカリが今　ゼロを生む
